ion over the dark squares. Black will often have to accept passivity if they want to survive our poison. White is scoring well in all the recommended lines (>55%) and I'm sure you will contribute to improving the scores even more!} cxd4 {Black's main choice by far.} (6... Bd7 7. Nc2 {and we are back into our territory.}) 7. cxd4 {The main tabiya.} Bb4+ 8. Bd2 Nxd4 $4 {The most common continuation in games of amateurs is a tactical blunder.} 9. Nxd4 Qxd4 (9... Bxa3 10. Bb5+ Kf8 11. bxa3 {and Black loses material.}) 10. Qa4+ {And Black loses a piece.} *

