... O-O-O 14. Qg4 h6 15. Qxh4 hxg5 16. Qxg5 {Dynamics helped Black gain a tiny initiative, but their position remains objectively lost.}) 14. Qh5 {[%csl Rh4,Rh8] And Black will lose material on the next move.} *

