[GameId "2180482215450729"]

9... O-O {Black should always be careful before castling on the kingside as they often allow the infamous Greek Gift sacrifice.} 10. Bxh7+ Kxh7 11. Ng5+ Kg8 12. Qh5 {And Black is doomed.} *

