[Black "Rook Lift #1"]
[Result "*"]
[SetUp "1"]
[FEN "r4rk1/ppqbnppp/4p3/3pP3/8/P2B2Q1/P4PPP/1RB2RK1 w - - 0 14"]
[PlyCount "1"]
[GameId "2180482215557232"]

{Now is the time to talk about rook lifts. We will see a few variations from the course where we use this powerful idea.} 14. Rb4 $1 {[%csl Gc1,Gd3,Gb4,Gg3,Rg7][%cal Gb4g4,Bh2h4,Bh4h5,Yc1h6,Bc1b2] A powerful move. The rook will join the attack via [g4] next. It is difficult to imagine how Black could survive this 'equal' position.} *

[Event "Dynamite 1.e4: Advance French for White"]
