[PlyCount "2"]
[GameId "2180482215565425"]

16... Re8 {Black is trying to make a luft for their king. In this type of positions, there are two rooks' moves we should always have in mind:} 17. Rc3 {[%cal Gb1c1,Gc3g3] The other one is [Rb3] with similar ideas. The rook is better placed on [c3] as it can be lifted to the kingside later or help to invade the 7th rank after doubling on the c-file.} *

