[PlyCount "1"]
[GameId "2180482215573618"]

12. h4 {[%cal Gh4h5,Gh5h6,Bh1h3,Bh3g3] A thematic idea in the French Defense. We push the h-pawn forward, creating space for the [h1]-rook to be activated via [h3]. From there, the rook can either move to [g3] or [h3] to apply pressure on Black's position. We will talk about this position in more details later in the course.} *

