the scores even more!} cxd4 {Black's main choice by far.} 7. cxd4 {The main tabiya.} Bb4+ 8. Bd2 Nxd4 $4 {The most common continuation in games of amateurs is a tactical blunder} 9. Nxd4 Qxd4 10. Qa4+ {And Black loses a piece.} *

